Class ParamGene

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jgapcustomised.Gene
      • com.ojcoleman.ahni.integration.ParamGene
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable

    public class ParamGene
extends Gene
    A generic parameter gene. A ParamGene may belong to a ParamCollection. A ParamGene may have an index within the ParamCollection.
